import React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react'; import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'; import Header from './Header'; import Footer from './Footer'; const Dashboard = () => { const [activeTab, setActiveTab] = useState('overview'); const [loading, setLoading] = useState(true); const [userData, setUserData] = useState({ name: 'Alex Johnson', email: 'alex.johnson@company.com', plan: 'Pro', usage: { agents: 5, automations: 12, apiCalls: '1.2M', storage: '4.5GB' } }); const [recentActivity, setRecentActivity] = useState([]); const [aiAgents, setAiAgents] = useState([]); const [automations, setAutomations] = useState([]); useEffect(() => { // Simulate loading data setTimeout(() => { setRecentActivity([ { id: 1, type: 'agent_created', title: 'Customer Support Agent', description: 'New AI agent created and deployed', time: '2 hours ago', icon: 'fas fa-robot', color: 'var(--primary)' }, { id: 2, type: 'automation_triggered', title: 'Lead Scoring Automation', description: 'Processed 245 leads automatically', time: '5 hours ago', icon: 'fas fa-bolt', color: '#4CAF50' }, { id: 3, type: 'api_usage', title: 'API Usage Alert', description: 'Reached 80% of monthly API limit', time: '1 day ago', icon: 'fas fa-chart-line', color: '#FF9800' }, { id: 4, type: 'integration_added', title: 'Slack Integration', description: 'Successfully connected to Slack workspace', time: '2 days ago', icon: 'fas fa-plug', color: '#9C27B0' } ]); setAiAgents([ { id: 1, name: 'Customer Support Pro', status: 'active', type: 'chatbot', usage: '85%', responses: '12.4K', avatar: 'CS', lastActive: '2 minutes ago' }, { id: 2, name: 'Lead Qualifier', status: 'active', type: 'analytics', usage: '67%', responses: '8.1K', avatar: 'LQ', lastActive: '1 hour ago' }, { id: 3, name: 'Content Generator', status: 'paused', type: 'content', usage: '42%', responses: '5.3K', avatar: 'CG', lastActive: '3 days ago' }, { id: 4, name: 'Data Analyzer', status: 'active', type: 'analytics', usage: '91%', responses: '15.7K', avatar: 'DA', lastActive: 'Just now' } ]); setAutomations([ { id: 1, name: 'Lead Scoring', status: 'running', triggers: 'Webhook, Email', lastRun: '5 minutes ago', successRate: '98%', runs: '1.2K' }, { id: 2, name: 'Customer Onboarding', status: 'running', triggers: 'Form Submission', lastRun: '2 hours ago', successRate: '95%', runs: '856' }, { id: 3, name: 'Invoice Processing', status: 'paused', triggers: 'Email Attachment', lastRun: '1 day ago', successRate: '92%', runs: '342' }, { id: 4, name: 'Social Media Scheduler', status: 'running', triggers: 'Time-based', lastRun: '30 minutes ago', successRate: '99%', runs: '2.1K' } ]); setLoading(false); }, 1500); }, []); const stats = [ { title: 'AI Agents', value: userData.usage.agents, total: 10, icon: 'fas fa-robot', color: 'var(--primary)', change: '+2 this month' }, { title: 'Active Automations', value: userData.usage.automations, total: 20, icon: 'fas fa-bolt', color: '#4CAF50', change: '+5 this week' }, { title: 'API Calls', value: userData.usage.apiCalls, total: '2M', icon: 'fas fa-chart-line', color: '#FF9800', change: '12% increase' }, { title: 'Storage Used', value: userData.usage.storage, total: '10GB', icon: 'fas fa-database', color: '#9C27B0', change: '45% utilized' } ]; const quickActions = [ { title: 'Create AI Agent', description: 'Build a new intelligent agent', icon: 'fas fa-plus', color: 'var(--primary)', link: '/ai-agents', action: 'create' }, { title: 'Setup Automation', description: 'Create workflow automation', icon: 'fas fa-bolt', color: '#4CAF50', link: '/automation', action: 'create' }, { title: 'View Analytics', description: 'Check performance metrics', icon: 'fas fa-chart-bar', color: '#FF9800', link: '/analytics', action: 'view' }, { title: 'API Documentation', description: 'Explore integration options', icon: 'fas fa-code', color: '#9C27B0', link: '/documentation', action: 'docs' } ]; if (loading) { return (
